-- Hiscox records claims from lost Malaysian plane, S.Korea ferry
-- By Richa Naidu in Bangalore
-- Tue May 06, 2014 02:25AM EDT
-- None



May 6 (Reuters) - British insurer Hiscox Ltd <HSX.L> said it recorded a "diverse list of losses" in the first quarter, including a small exposure to the Malaysia Airline <MASM.KL> flight MH370 that disappeared nearly two months ago and the Korean ferry that sunk last month.

